        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "看来“人造龙化计划”\\n也终于能进入到\\n下一阶段了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "是啊，批量生产\\n也终于有了眉目。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "没想到本以为是失败之作的\\n“Tf-997”竟然帮助我们\\n打开了局面。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "“龙锁”吗……是以前“博士”\\n研发的束缚龙并对其力量\\n加以利用的魔法对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "是的。永久融合型太不稳定了，\\n但是改为分离式合体型\\n似乎就可以解决问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "借助过去在“博士”的实验室\\n提取的魔力，我们还成功地\\n培养出了龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "接下来只需反复进行实验，\\n找到本体和龙甲之间的平衡即可。\\n所需的材料也已经有了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "嗯……那就开始实施\\n“龙锁兵计划”吧——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "“龙锁兵计划”……没想到\\n已经进行到了这一步。\\n看来我也得抓紧时间了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "过来，你给我进去！\\n老实待在里面吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "哇啊！好痛……\\n真是的，也太粗暴了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01",
                "120198_01",
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人们",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "啊，大家好啊。\\n我叫法尔吉德。\\n今后还请多多关照。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "打招呼就免了吧……\\n反正用不了几天我们就会\\n被拉去做实验，一命呜呼的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "别这么说嘛，\\n没准大家能一起活下来呢。\\n不要放弃希望嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "你傻啊。你是因为不知道这是哪里，\\n才会说出这种话。我就告诉你吧，\\n这里根本没有什么希望。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "也许用心去找就会发现了，\\n况且就算没有，我们自己\\n创造希望就好啦！一定会没事的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "你这家伙……逗我玩呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "给你点教训。\\n要是不想再吃苦头\\n就给我老实一点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "好痛啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "真是无妄之灾呢。你没事吧？\\n给，用这个冷敷一下\\n被打的地方吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "啊，嗯。谢谢你。\\n你是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "我叫杰克。\\n请多关照，法尔吉德。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "嗯，请多关照，杰克。\\n还好一上来就碰到你这样的好人。\\n看来我能在这里过得开心。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "开心？噗，哈哈哈哈！\\n你这个人真怪啊。\\n知道这里是什么地方吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "多少知道一点。\\n是一个叫“结社”的组织的\\n研究所之类的地方吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "嗯。我们都是实验素材，\\n似乎会被用到什么可怕的实验中。\\n被带走的人就再也没回来过。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "也就是说，我们能不能见到\\n明天的太阳也是个未知数。\\n这下你懂我们为什么不抱希望了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "明天有可能会死\\n并不能成为放弃\\n今天的希望的理由。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "你这家伙……真有意思。\\n不过我喜欢你的性格。\\n往后还请多关照啦，法尔吉德。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "逃跑？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "嗯，虽然不知道能不能成功，\\n但坐以待毙也无法改变现状。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "也对……与其等着当小白鼠，\\n还不如赌上一把。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "而且……我听守卫说，\\n这个设施周围的气氛\\n也充满了火药味。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "据说有一个叫阿德尔潘的人\\n在反抗“结社”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "大家都在说他很可能\\n会对这个设施下手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "既然是反抗“结社”，\\n不知道会不会与我们\\n站在同一战线……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "但据我所知，只要是在“结社”\\n设施里的，连女人和小孩\\n都会被他赶尽杀绝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "所以我也赞成逃跑。\\n那你有什么好主意吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "这个嘛，还没有……\\n我在想能不能\\n请你帮我一起想想……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "唉……我就知道你会这么说。\\n不过，这毕竟事关生死，\\n我就开动脑筋想想吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "洞？挖洞吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "这里的一部分地砖似乎能揭下来。\\n我们就从那里着手挖个洞，\\n只要能通向外面……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "也许就能逃出去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "只不过，我们必须争分夺秒。\\n毕竟现在甚至不知道\\n什么时候会被杀掉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "还有一个前提，我们需要得到\\n这个牢房里关的十几个人的协助。\\n应该说这一点或许最难办。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "没事的，\\n只要大家能重拾一些希望\\n就一定能做到！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "就这样，逃出“结社”的计划\\n开始进行。我们还得到了\\n被关在牢房里的人们的帮助。\\n事情看似一帆风顺，\\n但就在这时——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "喂，我要从你们这些人里\\n选出一个，荣升为“结社”\\n伟大研究的实验品。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "谁都行，\\n有没有人报名？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "实验品……\\n不就是要被杀吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "怎么会这样……\\n都到这一步了却……\\n我还不想死呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "……\\n那、那个！我来——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "唔！？杰、杰克？\\n为……什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120237_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杰克",
            "context": "抱歉，法尔吉德……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "杰克！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "啊，你醒啦，法尔吉德……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "杰克呢！\\n杰克去哪了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "杰克说他去当实验品，\\n跟他们走了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "怎么会……为什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "他说要是你不在了，\\n逃亡就不会成功，\\n能带给大家希望的只有你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "所以他就替我去了吗！\\n该死！为什么我总是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "被关起来的人",
            "context": "可是，我也……觉得杰克的\\n判断是正确的……就算是\\n为了杰克，我们也一定要成功。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "……\\n嗯……我一定会\\n把大家都救出去的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "只差……一点……\\n挖通了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "逃出来……了？\\n逃出来了！这里是设施外面！\\n太好了……太好了，杰克……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "不过现在可没空感动，\\n要赶紧把大家叫来才行。\\n得趁着晚上离开设施——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你想得也太美了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "结、“结社”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "你以为你们那点肤浅的想法\\n能瞒得过“结社”吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "为了避免再发生同样的事，\\n我就砍了你的头，\\n杀鸡儆猴好了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "等等。那家伙似乎是意志力相当\\n强大的素材。与其就这么杀了他，\\n不如用他来进行龙甲移植实验吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "把他抓起来，带去手术室。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "是，遵命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "对不起，大家……\\n对不起，杰克……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "开始手术——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "（唔、唔唔……有什么东西……\\n进入了我的身体……唔唔……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "（啊、啊啊……\\n哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
            "context": "失败？\\n我可听说手术成功了啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
            "context": "是的。本体没事，龙甲也没有失控，\\n所以一开始以为手术\\n进行得非常顺利，可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
            "context": "“龙锁”启动失败了，\\n无法装填龙甲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
            "context": "不过，我们已经找到了问题所在。\\n下次一定向您呈献\\n完美无缺的“龙锁兵”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
            "context": "嗯，我很期待。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "哎，这家伙怎么处理啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0085",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "失败之作已经没用了。\\n随便扔到哪里，自然会有人把他\\n和不顶用的龙甲一起处理掉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0086",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02",
                "120060_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "唔、唔唔……这里是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0087",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我、我……还活着？\\n原来……我还活着啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0088",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "这里是……和之前不同的牢房吗……\\n不知道其他人都怎么样了……\\n但愿他们没遭殃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0089",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "怎、怎么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0090",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "“结社”兵",
            "context": "喂，快来人支援！\\n是那家伙！\\n那家伙——阿德尔潘出现了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0091",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "阿、阿德尔潘？\\n我记得阿德尔潘是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0092",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "要破坏“结社”的设施、\\n把里面的人赶尽杀绝的\\n那个人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0093",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "大家有危险！我得立刻\\n去救他们才行！得想一个\\n从这里脱身的办法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0094",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "破坏墙壁！？掰弯铁栏！？\\n行不通，我也没有那种力气。\\n挖洞！不对，哪有那个时间啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0095",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "没事的。别放弃，还有希望。\\n希望一定就藏在某处……\\n别放弃，还有希望。别放弃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0096",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "要我帮你一把吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0097",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "要，谢谢你！\\n咦……诶诶！？你、你是谁！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0098",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "真没礼貌。我们是搭档……\\n不，是一心同体的关系啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0099",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "你……你是龙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0100",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我是作为龙锁兵龙甲\\n而被“结社”那帮人\\n培养出来的模拟龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0101",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "那帮人叫我“巴巴托斯B组件”，\\n不过我可不喜欢这名字。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0102",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "算了，现在先不说这些。\\n所以你打算怎么做？\\n我能帮你从这里逃出去哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0103",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "那就拜托你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0104",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不假思索地回答啊。\\n你确定？万一我之后\\n向你索要回报呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0105",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "只要是我能给的，\\n什么都可以给你。只要你能\\n借我救出大家的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0106",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不知道你是胆子大还是单纯的傻。\\n算了，我倒是不讨厌你这种性格。\\n那我们就开始吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0107",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "“龙锁装填”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0108",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "究竟发生了什么……\\n咦，怎么回事！？\\n我、我的手臂……这是什么啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0109",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这见鬼的力量是“结社”\\n那群家伙给我们的……\\n叫“龙锁装填”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0110",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊！我的右手说话了！？\\n那、那个……你难道是\\n巴巴托斯……B组件？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0111",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我不是说过不喜欢这个名字吗。\\n总之你现在已经具备了\\n高于一般龙的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0112",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "高于龙的力量……\\n我知道了，谢谢你。\\n唔……巴比！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0113",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "巴、巴比！？\\n我的名字吗！？开什么玩笑，\\n我才不要这么随便的名字！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0114",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "简单易懂，多好的名字啊。\\n总之先用这股力量破坏牢房……\\n哈啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0115",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "真、真的好厉害啊，这股力量……\\n这下也许就能救出大家了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0116",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "喂，现在可不是偷着乐的时候！\\n有人……不，是有什么东西在靠近！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0117",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "唔！？你这家伙，那副模样……\\n原来如此，你就是格蕾丝\\n提到过的“龙锁兵”吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0118",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "他的身体……和我一样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0119",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "不，不一样。他是早期开发的\\n永久融合类型。Tf-997……\\n是阿德尔潘！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0120",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "阿德尔潘！？他就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0121",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "你那受到诅咒的力量\\n不可以被释放出来。\\n你必须在这里消失。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0122",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "该死……喂！现在的你\\n和他比起来，经验相差悬殊！\\n我们赢不了的，准备逃跑！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0123",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "不行！要是我逃走了，\\n这里的其他人也会被杀！\\n所以我必须要面对他！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0124",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "你做好觉悟了吗。既然如此，\\n就为被这股禁忌的力量\\n所迷惑的自己感到后悔吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0125",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我要保护大家！\\n保护大家啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0126",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "好大的威力……看来不能\\n因为他是复制品\\n就小看了他……但是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0127",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "呃啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0128",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "看来你还无法控制自己的力量。\\n就趁现在和你做个了断吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0129",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "可、可恶！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0130",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "阿德尔潘！你在做什么！？\\n我们没时间了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0131",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "格蕾丝，我现在正在对付\\n龙锁兵。这家伙的确很危险，\\n我们不能放任他不管……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0132",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "龙锁兵？怎么会呢。\\n那应该还没有完成才对……\\n诶！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0133",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "“龙锁装填”成功了？\\n之前明明因为“龙锁”\\n无法启动而失败了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0134",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "不是无法启动，\\n而是我没有启动。\\n因为我不想听命于“结社”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0135",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "巴巴托斯B组件说话了！？\\n真是难以置信……\\n都是些意料之外的状况……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0136",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "不过听你的语气，\\n你不打算听命于“结社”？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0137",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "那当然！被他们擅自\\n鼓捣一通身体之后，\\n谁会乖乖听他们的话啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0138",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "这样啊……我说，阿德尔潘。\\n他们看起来不是我们的敌人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0139",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "似乎是这样没错……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0140",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "等、等一下。你们不是\\n要袭击“结社”的设施，\\n把这里的人都赶尽杀绝吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0141",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "什么，\\n这也太危言耸听了吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0142",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "有必要的话就杀。但是“结社”\\n设施里的大部分人都是\\n被关起来的，我们要解救这些人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0143",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "那么，我们……不必对战了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0144",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "是啊。倒不如说希望你们\\n能助我们一臂之力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0145",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "发生什么事了吗，格蕾丝？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0146",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "是啊，“结社”已经决定放弃这里。\\n他们正准备摧毁设施\\n并销毁实验素材。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0147",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110059_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "格蕾丝",
            "context": "放任不管的话就真成赶尽杀绝了。\\n不过我想尽可能地\\n解救那些被关起来的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0148",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "啧，该死的“结社”。\\n真是狗改不了吃屎。\\n喂，我说你——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0149",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "啊，我叫……法尔吉德。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0150",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110262_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿德尔潘",
            "context": "如果你有即使赌上性命\\n也想保护的东西，就助我们\\n一臂之力吧，法尔吉德。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0151",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "好、好的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22216_01_0152",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}